OL,3,CSupreme Court to issue ruling in
OL,4,Cdispute over definition of a woman
OL,6,FThe UK Supreme Court is set to rule on
OL,7,Fthe legal definition of a woman,
OL,8,Ffollowing a challenge brought by
OL,9,Fwomen's rights campaigners.
OL,11,FThe ruling follows a series of
OL,12,Fchallenges brought by the campaign
OL,13,Fgroup, For Women Scotland (FWS), over
OL,14,Fthe definition of "woman" in Scottish
OL,15,Flegislation mandating 50% female
OL,16,Frepresentation on public boards.
