OL,3,CSupreme Court to issue ruling in
OL,4,Cdispute over definition of a woman
OL,6,FFollowing the challenge, the Scottish
OL,7,FGovernment dropped the definition from
OL,8,Fthe act and issued revised statutory
OL,9,Fguidance ` essentially, advice on how
OL,10,Fto comply with the law.
OL,12,FThis stated that under the 2018 Act
OL,13,Fthe definition of a woman was the same
OL,14,Fas that set out in the Equality Act
OL,15,F2010, and also that a person with a
OL,16,FGRC recognising their gender as female
OL,17,Fhad the sex of a woman.
