OL,3,CSupreme Court to issue ruling in
OL,4,Cdispute over definition of a woman
OL,6,FFWS challenged this revised guidance
OL,7,Fon the grounds sex under the Equality
OL,8,FAct referred to its biological
OL,9,Fmeaning, and the Government was
OL,10,Foverstepping its powers by effectively
OL,11,Fredefining the meaning of "woman".
OL,13,FHowever, its challenge was rejected by
OL,14,Fthe Court of Session's Outer House on
OL,15,FDecember 13 2022.
OL,17,FThe Inner House upheld that decision
OL,18,Fon November 1 2023 ` but did grant FWS
OL,19,Fpermission to appeal to the UK Supreme
OL,20,FCourt.
