OL,3,CSupreme Court to issue ruling in
OL,4,Cdispute over definition of a woman
OL,6,FThe appeal at the Supreme Court before
OL,7,FLord Reed, Lord Hodge, Lord Lloyd-
OL,8,FJones, Lady Rose and Lady Simler was
OL,9,Fheard last November and, after the two-
OL,10,Fday hearing, the judges said they
OL,11,Fwould "take time to consider very
OL,12,Fcarefully" before issuing their
OL,13,Fjudgment on April 16.
