OL,6,FShe added: "We submit there are only
OL,7,Ftwo sexes or genders, and a person
OL,8,Fwhose sex becomes that of a man or
OL,9,Fwoman in consequence of a GRC belongs
OL,10,Fto that sex, and will have the
OL,11,Fprotection afforded under the Equality
OL,12,FAct".
OL,14,FThe Scottish Government said they were
OL,15,Funable to comment on live legal
OL,16,Fproceedings.
